<opml version="2.0" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.dlsciences.org/frameworks/fields" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.dlsciences.org/frameworks/fields http://nldr.library.ucar.edu/metadata/osm/1.1/schemas/fields/non-vocab-fields.xsd">
	<head>
		<title>Total Pages</title>
		<concept language="en-us" metaFormat="osm" metaVersion="1.1" text="Total Pages" audience="submission" path="/record/general/pageTotal" deftn="The total number of pages that comprise a resource."/>
	</head>
	 <bestPractices>
		<practice>This field is optional.</practice> 
		<practice>Use only Arabic numerals.</practice> 
		<practice>Use for entire journals, magazines, newsletters, proceedings, books, encyclopedias technical notes or reports.</practice> 
		 <practice>Do not precede or follow the numerals with 'pp.,' 'total pages,' or any other text.</practice> 
		 <practice>Do not use this field for articles (journal, magazine, newsletter, proceedings or encyclopedia entries), book chapters, book forewords, book reviews, technical notes or bibliographies/indexes.</practice> 
		 <practice>Do not preface or follow the pages with a number sign or any abbreviations.</practice> 
	 </bestPractices>
</opml>
